OL,3,CWoman killed when unsecured load fell
OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for causing
OL,7,Fdeath by dangerous driving after an
OL,8,Funsecured load he was transporting
OL,9,Ffell on a woman's car, causing her
OL,10,F"catastrophic" injuries.
OL,12,FJessica Allman, who was 34 and from
OL,13,FNewquay, worked as a "Young People
OL,14,FAdviser", promoting good mental health
OL,15,Fthrough personal development,
OL,16,Feducation and employment.
OL,18,FOn the 19 July 2022, she left Costa
OL,19,FCoffee in Helston with the intention
OL,20,Fof driving to her next work
OL,21,Fappointment in Pool.
