OL,3,CWoman killed when unsecured load fell
OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,FHowever, she never made it to her
OL,7,Fdestination. On the B3297 at Burras, a
OL,8,Fdrilling rig flew off a trailer
OL,9,Ftravelling in the opposite direction
OL,10,Fand hit her Fiat Punto.
OL,12,FLiam Smith, who is 35 and from
OL,13,FRoselidden Park in Helston, was jailed
OL,14,Ffor five years and four months at
OL,15,FTruro Crown Court after previously
OL,16,Fpleading guilty to causing the death
OL,17,Fof Jessica Allman by dangerous driving.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
