OL,3,CWoman killed when unsecured load fell
OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,FAt Truro Crown Court, Smith was also
OL,7,Fdisqualified from driving and must
OL,8,Ftake an extended re-test to regain his
OL,9,Flicence.
OL,11,FThe court heard how on 19 July 2022
OL,12,FSmith was in Newquay when he loaded a
OL,13,FBeretta T24 hydraulic drilling rig
OL,14,Fonto a two axel Bateson platform
OL,15,Ftrailer.
OL,17,FThe trailer was attached to a white
OL,18,FFord Ranger belonging to Smith's
OL,19,Femployer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
