OL,3,CWoman killed when unsecured load fell
OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,FSmith secured the drilling rig by
OL,7,Fplacing one ratchet strap over the
OL,8,Fmast and attached it to the welded
OL,9,Feyelets on the trailer. Despite being
OL,10,Fassisted by a colleague, it was
OL,11,FSmith's responsibility to ensure the
OL,12,Frig was correctly secured.
OL,14,FThe Ford Ranger was spotted on CCTV at
OL,15,FCallestick and then on the A30 with
OL,16,Fthe single ratchet strap visible over
OL,17,Fthe drilling rig.
OL,19,FHowever, at around 1pm, Smith stopped
OL,20,Fat Macsalvors in Redruth and failed to
OL,21,Fcheck the load prior to leaving.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
