OL,3,CWoman killed when unsecured load fell
OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,FCCTV from the location shows the Ford
OL,7,FRanger, trailer and drilling rig in
OL,8,Fthe carpark, but crucially no ratchet
OL,9,Fstrap was visible securing the
OL,10,Fdrilling rig.
OL,12,FSmith then continued on the B3297
OL,13,Ftowards Helston, entering the area of
OL,14,FBurras at around 1.30pm.
OL,16,FAs Smith drove through Burras and
OL,17,Ftried to negotiate a left-hand bend,
OL,18,Fthe drilling rig became unstable and
OL,19,Ffell from the offside of the trailer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
