OL,3,CWoman killed when unsecured load fell
OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,FThe rig struck the Fiat Punto,
OL,7,Ftragically causing Jessica
OL,8,Fcatastrophic unsurvivable injuries.
OL,10,FThe Ford Ranger and trailer continued
OL,11,Fa short distance up the road where it
OL,12,Fcame to a stop.
OL,14,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,15,Fand investigating officers noted an
OL,16,Fold and worn ratchet strap broken into
OL,17,Ftwo pieces.
OL,19,FThere were an additional seven straps
OL,20,Favailable to Smith within the vehicle
OL,21,Fand trailer which he chose not to use.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
