OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,FSeveral webbing straps were in an
OL,7,Fadvanced stated of wear and should
OL,8,Fhave been discarded long before the
OL,9,Fcollision. There was evidence of poor
OL,10,Fpractice by Smith relating to the
OL,11,Ffixing of the webbing straps.
OL,13,FWhen weighed, the Ford Ranger, trailer
OL,14,Fand drilling rig exceeded combined
OL,15,Fweight restrictions, which would have
OL,16,Fcontributed to the vehicle instability
OL,17,Fwhen cornering.
OL,19,F'This collision was entirely
OL,20,Fpreventable' - Police Chief
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
