OL,6,FDC Helen Lentern from the Serious
OL,7,FCollisions Investigation Team, said:
OL,8,F"This collision was the culmination of
OL,9,FSmith's wholesale disregard of the
OL,10,Fsecurity of the load and safety of
OL,11,Fother road users.
OL,13,F"If an adequate number of lashings had
OL,14,Fbeen used in conjunction with
OL,15,Fblocking, then the failure of a single
OL,16,Fstrap should not have results in load
OL,17,Fmovement.
