OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1765459887
OL,3,CWoman killed when unsecured load fell
OL,4,Coff trailer and hit her car
OL,6,F"The single strap used by Smith was in
OL,7,Fan advance state of wear and should
OL,8,Fhave been discarded long before this
OL,9,Fcollision.
OL,11,F"Since May 2022, it has been a
OL,12,Frequirement in the Categorisation of
OL,13,FVehicle Defects to secure heavy plant
OL,14,Fthrough a combination of loading or
OL,15,Fpacking to a bulkhead and a minimum of
OL,16,Ffour direct lashings.
OL,18,F"This collision was entirely
OL,19,Fpreventable and Jessica Allman was a
OL,20,Fblameless member of the public.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
