OL,6,F"Jessica had the misfortune of being
OL,7,Fin the wrong place at the wrong time
OL,8,Fas she went about her working day.
OL,9,FNothing will ever bring Jessica back
OL,10,Fbut we hope her family are now able to
OL,11,Ffeel some closure following the
OL,12,Fconclusion of the case".
